title: Sibling Watchery - Season 14: Meet the Queens
description:
On this week's episode of Sibling Watchery, Bob is back from his surgery and ready to dive into Season 14 of Drag Race with Monét! The two get right to discussing the newest cast of queens, complaining about the lack of comedy chops among the cast overall. Bob names Cornbread their favorite queen so far, Monét reminds everyone of the importance of 'committing to the bit', and they name the new Nickelback of Drag Race.
